OL,3,CMasseur appears in court to deny 55
OL,4,Csexual offences against clients
OL,6,FAn osteopath and masseur has appeared
OL,7,Fin court to deny 55 sexual offences
OL,8,Frelating to 14 female clients.
OL,10,FTerence McBrien, 72, of Alnwick,
OL,11,FNorthumberland, was before Newcastle
OL,12,FCrown Court on Thursday (16 April) for
OL,13,Fa hearing lasting about an hour.
OL,15,FIt took the court clerk more than 16
OL,16,Fminutes to read out all 55 charges
OL,17,Fwhich comprise one count of attempted
OL,18,Frape, seven counts of sexual assault
OL,19,Fby penetration, 34 counts of sexual
OL,20,Fassault by touching, and 13 counts of
OL,21,Fvoyeurism.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
