CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1776611465
OL,3,CMasseur appears in court to deny 55
OL,4,Csexual offences against clients
OL,6,FThe charges relate to 14 women who
OL,7,Fengaged with him while he offered
OL,8,Fservices as a masseur or osteopath,
OL,9,FKama Melly KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,10,Fcourt.
OL,12,FThe allegations date between 2011 and
OL,13,F2021.
OL,15,FMcBrien answered "not guilty" in a
OL,16,Fclear voice to each of the charges.
OL,18,FJudge Edward Bindloss told McBrien
OL,19,Fthat a trial lasting up to four months
OL,20,Fwill take place from 19 April 2027.
